data.text: You ever stumble a bit of Internet Content so good that you think, ‘Oh, this must have only just come out! Something this good I would have seen multiple times by now if it was any older than just a few days. I have to share it with others!’ Well imagine the stupid expression on my gobsmacked face when I found this incredible parody/homage to Tarantino’s Kill Bill shared on Reddit, and I followed it through to YouTube, only to see when it was released. What the hell?! What else have I been missing?! Was anyone else aware of this?
